1
00:00:00,760 --> 00:00:02,440
So, who are we actually sending?

2
00:00:02,840 --> 00:00:04,880
Aren't you on the track team? You should run.

3
00:00:05,120 --> 00:00:06,480
Me?

4
00:00:06,480 --> 00:00:07,120
What about you?

5
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:08,120
Count me out.

6
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:09,600
Just do it!

7
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:10,000
So, should I sign up?

8
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Yeah, go for it.

9
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:12,760
For real? You're sure I should sign up?

10
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:14,280
Do it! Go run!

11
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,360
Iijima Hinata!

12
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:16,480
Right!

13
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:21,760
I'm going to be the hero?

14
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,760
Go be the hero already.

15
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:27,560
We're still two people short.

16
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:31,240
Huh?

17
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:32,240
What are you doing?

18
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:35,800
Is Iijima Hinata competing?

19
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:38,040
How about asking...

20
00:00:38,080 --> 00:00:39,160
Can I run too?

21
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:42,040
We'd love to have you.

22
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:43,040
But is your injury okay?

23
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,200
Yeah...

24
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:47,120
I checked with my doctor. It's fine.

25
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,200
Besides...

26
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:51,920
It's been so long.

27
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,640
I really want to run with everyone again.

28
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,320
Then I'm in too.

29
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,320
Huh?

30
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,120
Hey, stop copying me.

31
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,760
You're always following Iijima Hinata around.

32
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:10,160
One, two, three, four.

33
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:12,200
Ah! I give up, I give up!

34
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,520
Haven't run in a while, have you?

35
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,320
If you don't stretch, your injury will flare up again.

36
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:18,800
Forcing a stretch is bad for you!

37
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,480
This is all for my little brother.

38
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,840
Feel the power of a big brother!

39
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,280
Take this!

40
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,680
Whoa!

41
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,320
Man, I'm exhausted!

42
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,560
It's been ages since I've worked up a sweat like this.

43
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,560
Here!

44
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,240
As expected from the track team.

45
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,720
You're fast.

46
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,560
Hey, what are you doing?

47
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,400
Huh?

48
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,520
That's my water bottle.

49
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,320
Don't like indirect kisses?

50
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,760
So innocent. How cute.

51
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,760
So annoying.
